title: D.I.Y. 0-60 R-CADE NEED FOR SPEED SHIFT
description: Here is a set of files that are in a PDF format.I seen them and wanted to share them on here for everyone. It is a Sit down simulator that you can add a PC, PS3,Wii,Xbox 360 or any game system. Once it is built, you can add any decals to the side or just paint them. It would be a great project to add to any man cave or just to sit in the den somewhere.
